{
  "stem": "10768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since we were not so well off, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was, it was a problem.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So whatever we were making helped a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since my mother was working, whoever was working later on was getting, let's say, a half a pound of bread daily.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, there was the stamp system.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the Russians immediately made a high school in our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since I had a pretty good schooling and a lot of courses I took privately-- like algebra, some sciences-- I went to the high school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And immediately, I, I received-- not immediately, but let's say within two, three weeks-- I received a high school diploma.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At the same time, maybe perhaps, because our town was on the boundary, the Russians have established a very, I would say, wide health care system, considering the size of our town.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First of all, because it was on the boundary, there were a lot of Russian, Russian dignitaries.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or they were on all the supervisory position in the Department of Health, in the Department of Commerce.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- so because of that, was a high school right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a-- a hospital was made, which was taken away from nuns.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The nuns had sort of like a little clinic, a Catholic clinic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They established there a hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was another clinic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, where the clinic was previously, was established a hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A clinic was opened where by coincidence, one of our relatives was the head doctor of the clinic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was nice enough to give me a job, first in the clinic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then they opened a department-- at the health department, they opened a department of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] preventive, to prevent illnesses, vaccination.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
